Replaces the HUD with a beautiful, simple: Green, Dark & White HUD; [Server-Side]

Elements Replaced:

[code]
- All Ammo Types
- HP
- Armor
- Syringe
- Welder
- Text Colors
- Border/Box Colors
- Wave Indicator
- Time Indicator
- Trader Arrow
- Magazine Clip
- Grenades
- PipeBombs
- Perk Stars/Levels
- Inventory Overlay
[/code]

Elements Fixed:

[code]
- All Text alignments
- All Icons aligned on same Y-Axis
- Fix for Weight numbers being so wonky from TWI code (Made them as Numeric Widgets)
[/code]

Anything else that I've forgot about :D

Elements that haven't been changed yet:

[code]
- Perk Icons[/strike]
[/code]

[H1][b][u]Notes[/u][/b][/H1]

For Players:

- Once enabled, anyone who joins your server will also have this HUD.
- Tested with ServerPerks
- NOT Tested with ScrN Balance!

For Devs:

- This 'Might' have issues with any other mod or mutator that touches HUDKillingFloor Class.

[H1][b][u]Number Of Files[/u][/b][/H1]

